
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>Sabal Park — Development Budget Board</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f6f8;
    --panel: #ffffff;
    --ink: #1a1f2b;
    --muted: #6b7280;
    --line: #e5e7eb;
    --accent: #1e3a8a;
    --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
    --good: #047857;
    --warn: #b45309;
    --danger: #b91c1c;
    --hover: #f3f4f6;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }

  header.top {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  header.top h1 { margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 20px; color: var(--accent); }
  header.top .sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
  .save-indicator {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--good);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: #ecfdf5;
    border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .save-indicator.saving { color: var(--warn); background: #fffbeb; border-color: #fde68a; }

  .grid-2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) { .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .panel {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .panel h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* assumption rows */
  .assump-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
  }
  .assump-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .assump-row label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
  .assump-row input {
    text-align: right;
    width: 130px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font: inherit;
    background: var(--panel);
  }
  .assump-row input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-soft); }
  .assump-row .computed {
    text-align: right;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding-right: 8px;
  }

  /* budget table */
  .budget-panel { padding: 0; overflow: hidden; }
  .budget-header {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .budget-header h2 { margin: 0; border: none; padding: 0; }
  .btn {
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--panel);
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .btn:hover { background: var(--hover); }
  .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: white; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .btn.primary:hover { background: #172554; }
  .btn.small { padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 11px; }
  .btn.danger { color: var(--danger); border-color: #fecaca; }
  .btn.danger:hover { background: #fee2e2; }

  table.budget {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  table.budget th {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: #fafbfc;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
  }
  table.budget td {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  table.budget tr.category-row td {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
  }
  table.budget tr.category-row .cat-total {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  table.budget tr.add-row td {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }

  /* editable inputs in table */
  table.budget input {
    font: inherit;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    background: transparent;
    padding: 4px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  table.budget input:hover { border-color: var(--line); background: white; }
  table.budget input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-soft);
  }
  table.budget input.qty, table.budget input.unit, table.budget input.unit-cost {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  table.budget input.unit { text-align: center; width: 60px; }
  table.budget td.total {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  table.budget td.total.auto {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* column widths */
  .col-desc { width: 42%; }
  .col-qty { width: 90px; }
  .col-unit { width: 70px; }
  .col-unit-cost { width: 120px; }
  .col-total { width: 140px; }
  .col-action { width: 50px; text-align: center; }

  /* summary */
  .summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

  .returns-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .returns-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 22px 0 8px 2px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .metric-good { color: var(--good); }
  .metric-warn { color: var(--warn); }
  .metric-bad { color: var(--danger); }

  .summary-card .sub-val {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .summary-card.accent .sub-val { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
  .summary-card {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
  }
  .summary-card .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .summary-card .value {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .summary-card.accent { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .summary-card.accent .label, .summary-card.accent .value { color: white; }

  .notes {
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: #fffbeb;
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: #78350f;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .actions-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* row delete button */
  .row-del {
    color: var(--danger);
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.4;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  tr:hover .row-del { opacity: 1; }
  .row-del:hover { background: #fee2e2; }

  /* commission auto row */
  .auto-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 9px;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-left: 6px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header class="top">
    <div>
      <h1>Sabal Park — Development Budget Board</h1>
      <div class="sub">3,600 SF Retail Strip Center · 3 tenants @ 1,200 SF · E MLK Jr. Blvd & Cragmont Dr, Tampa</div>
    </div>
    <div class="save-indicator" id="saveInd">Saved</div>
  </header>

  <div class="actions-bar">
    <button class="btn" id="addCategoryBtn">+ Add Category</button>
    <button class="btn" id="resetBtn">Reset to Default</button>
    <button class="btn" id="exportBtn">Export CSV</button>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-3">
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Project Assumptions</h2>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Building Size (SF)</label>
        <input type="number" id="bldgSF" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Number of Tenants</label>
        <input type="number" id="numTenants" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Avg SF / Tenant</label>
        <div class="computed" id="sfPerTenant">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Base Rent ($/SF/yr, Year 1)</label>
        <input type="number" id="baseRent" step="0.25" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Annual Rent Escalation (%)</label>
        <input type="number" id="escalation" step="0.1" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Commission Rate (%)</label>
        <input type="number" id="commRate" step="0.25" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Construction Period (months)</label>
        <input type="number" id="constrMonths" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h2>NOI & Operating</h2>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Year 1 Gross Rent (all tenants)</label>
        <div class="computed" id="y1Rent">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>10-Year Base Rent (cumulative)</label>
        <div class="computed" id="tenYrRent">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Leasing Commission (auto)</label>
        <div class="computed" id="commCalc">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Vacancy / Collection Loss (%)</label>
        <input type="number" id="vacancy" step="0.25" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Management Fee (% of EGI)</label>
        <input type="number" id="mgmtFee" step="0.25" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Replacement Reserves ($/SF)</label>
        <input type="number" id="reserves" step="0.05" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label><strong>Stabilized NOI (Year 1)</strong></label>
        <div class="computed" id="noi">—</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Debt & Exit</h2>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Loan Amount</label>
        <input type="number" id="loanAmt" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Interest Rate (%)</label>
        <input type="number" id="intRate" step="0.125" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Amortization (years)</label>
        <input type="number" id="amort" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Annual Debt Service</label>
        <div class="computed" id="debtSvc">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Exit Cap Rate (%)</label>
        <input type="number" id="exitCap" step="0.05" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Cost of Sale (%)</label>
        <input type="number" id="costSale" step="0.25" />
      </div>
      <div class="assump-row">
        <label>Equity Required</label>
        <div class="computed" id="equityReq">—</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel budget-panel">
    <div class="budget-header">
      <h2>Development Budget — Line Items</h2>
      <div style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px;">Click any cell to edit · All changes auto-save</div>
    </div>
    <table class="budget" id="budgetTable">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="col-desc">Description</th>
          <th class="col-qty" style="text-align:right;">Qty</th>
          <th class="col-unit" style="text-align:center;">Unit</th>
          <th class="col-unit-cost" style="text-align:right;">Unit Cost</th>
          <th class="col-total" style="text-align:right;">Total</th>
          <th class="col-action"></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="budgetBody"></tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Cost Summary</div>
  <div class="summary-grid">
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Hard Costs</div>
      <div class="value" id="hardTotal">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Soft Costs</div>
      <div class="value" id="softTotal">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Total Project Cost / SF</div>
      <div class="value" id="costPSF">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card accent">
      <div class="label">Total Development Cost</div>
      <div class="value" id="grandTotal">—</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Returns & Debt Metrics</div>
  <div class="returns-grid">
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Return on Cost (Yield)</div>
      <div class="value" id="roc">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="rocSub">NOI ÷ Total Dev Cost</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">DSCR</div>
      <div class="value" id="dscr">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="dscrSub">NOI ÷ Annual Debt Service</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Loan to Cost (LTC)</div>
      <div class="value" id="ltc">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="ltcSub">Loan ÷ Total Dev Cost</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Loan to Value (LTV)</div>
      <div class="value" id="ltv">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="ltvSub">Loan ÷ As-Complete Value</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Exit / Sale Analysis</div>
  <div class="returns-grid">
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">As-Complete Value (Sale Price)</div>
      <div class="value" id="salePrice">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="salePriceSub">NOI ÷ Exit Cap</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Cost of Sale</div>
      <div class="value" id="costOfSaleVal">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="costOfSaleSub">% of Sale Price</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="label">Net Sale Proceeds</div>
      <div class="value" id="netSale">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="netSaleSub">Sale − Cost of Sale</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card accent">
      <div class="label">Development Profit</div>
      <div class="value" id="profit">—</div>
      <div class="sub-val" id="profitSub">Margin %</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="notes">
    <strong>Notes:</strong> Hard costs based on Leonard Contractors budget dated Apr 8, 2026. Leasing commission auto-calculates as Commission Rate × 10-Year Base Rent (with annual escalations compounded). Loan defaults mirror the Valley Bank term sheet: $1,590,000, 25-yr am, 5.75% (T5+250bps stabilized floor, yrs 3–7). NOI = Gross Rent − Vacancy − Management Fee − Replacement Reserves. Color coding: <span class="metric-good">green</span> = meets target, <span class="metric-warn">amber</span> = close, <span class="metric-bad">red</span> = miss. DSCR target ≥1.25x (Valley covenant), LTC ≤75%, LTV ≤70%, ROC ≥8%.
  </div>

</div>

